### 1. Admin tạo Khung giờ 1 (08:00 - 09:00)
POST http://localhost:8080/api/v1/admin/slots
Authorization: Bearer {{adminToken}}
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "startTime": "08:00:00",
  "endTime": "09:00:00"
}

### 2. Admin tạo Khung giờ 2 (09:00 - 10:00)
POST http://localhost:8080/api/v1/admin/slots
Authorization: Bearer {{adminToken}}
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "startTime": "09:00:00",
  "endTime": "10:00:00"
}

### 3. Khách xem các khung giờ còn trống (AVAILABLE)
GET http://localhost:8080/api/v1/slots/available

### 4. Admin xem danh sách tất cả khung giờ
GET http://localhost:8080/api/v1/admin/slots
Authorization: Bearer {{adminToken}}